name: The Gate of KaBa
description:
Mvdra, Svnya, and Mvdja are called The Seeds of Wanderer. Born from one of the greater divinity in JAGADJIGO, Dzat Azalia. 

Azalia lost her divinity power after creating them. She becomes a mere creature with only healing power. She receives a sentence from another Dzat without resistance, because of her fault. She is exiled to the region of death, a place where many dark souls hunt for prey, it is called The Gate of KaBa.

The name itself is the epithet of the region keeper, a colossal mythological creature with giant horns to incarcerate Azalia.

Mvdra with his weapon, Ishtar. A sword with Hieropine spell power, on his way to defeat KaBa and retrieve his queen to the safest place.
